âœ… Version 1: Clean & Professional
plantuml
@startuml
title <b>CropSense: Farm Advisory System</b>

|Farmer|
start
:Access Farm Dashboard;
|IoT Sensors|
:Collect Soil Moisture Data;
:Collect Temperature Data;
:Collect Humidity Data;
:Send Data to Cloud;
|CropSense System|
:Store in weather_data Database;
:Run Analysis Procedure;

if (Low rainfall in last 5 days?) then (yes)
  :Generate Irrigation Advisory;
  -> High Priority;
else (no)
  if (High temperature detected?) then (yes)
    :Generate Heat Warning Advisory;
    -> Medium Priority;
  else (no)
    :Normal Conditions - No Advisory;
    detach
  endif
endif

|Notification Service|
if (Severity >= HIGH?) then (yes)
  :Send SMS Alert to Farmer;
  :Send Email Report;
else (no)
  :Send Email Notification;
endif

|Farmer|
:Receive Advisory on Dashboard;
:Review Recommendations;
:Take Action if needed;
stop
@enduml```
